ill accent the sofa maybe you need an area rug to cover up that hideous stain on the floor that you cannot get rid of whatever the reason for needing or wanting an area rug know that we have the selection and the price that will make you happy shop online at wayfair to find an area or throw rug that will match the décor and style of any room – whether it is for a dining room kitchen bedroom or living room floor when looking to buy your new area rug there are a few things to consider here are a few commonly asked questions how do i know what size area rug to buy first you should consider the size and the shape of your room if you have a round room with circular furniture a round rug would be right for you if you have all square furniture in a square room a square area rug is best for you from here you want to make sure the rug is big enough to be placed on the ground and not completely covered by any furniture thats placed on top of it when in doubt order a rug thats a little bit bigger to make sure your sofa sitting chairs bed or any other piece of furniture doesn’t hide the area rug for a more detailed guide on this you can read our area rug size guide which area rug material is right for my space popular area rugs include sheepskin rugs cotton rugs wool rugs braided rugs natural fiber rugs and more when picking the right style rug think about the purpose of your room is the room used a lot with a considerable amount of foot traffic and furniture movement if so you may want to opt for a wool or cotton rug as they are much more durable than a natural fiber or sea grass rug put a sheepskin rug in your bedroom or sitting rooms to help achieve that warm glam look design options are endless with fun and creative area rugs how to i find the perfect area rug to buy area rugs its best to use the filters on the left to narrow your selection if youre looking for the popular  x  rug for example you can hit the  to  filter to see only the rugs that are the right size for your space similarly you can filter by the colours of the area rug shape pattern material and more also be aware that most of the area rugs we offer come in multiple sizes look for the more options link beneath the picture in these cases the site will list a price range rather than a single fixed price representing the cost of different sizes or shapes of the rug cat area rug tip cats that have not been declawed may want to sharpen their claws on your area rug it has been observed that cats strongly prefer wool rugs for claw sharpening and are less interested in synthetics particularly when cat tree or scratching post is available nearby whether you are looking for a wool rug rag rug braided rug or oriental rug we have it all we even have faux animal rugs which include grizzly bears black bears pandas and tigers – a fun option for kids choose from a variety of different colours styles and patterns sure to blend in nicely with your home décorwayfairca features a wide selection of area rugs so that you can find the perfect one for your home whether you live in calgary toronto vancouver or somewhere else youll discover a variety of area rugs options from top brand like laurel foundry modern farmhouse and red barrel studio shop through our store and discover how great shopping online for area rugs and everything else for your home can be at wayfairca related searches area rugs clearance front entry rugs bedroom rugs shaggy area rugs persian rug navy rug sponsored links advertisement feedback get it fast express shipping postal code   change rug size  x   x   x   x   x   x   x   x   x   x     roundsquare    roundsquare    roundsquare    roundsquare  runner  runner  runner  runner   runner sample colour price per item under cad  cad  to  cad  to  cad  to  cad  to  cad   above  to  material wool synthetics polypropylene polyester cotton jute  sisal silk natural fibres cowhide leather chenille bamboo rayon  seagrass sheepskin microfiber pile height flat  thin  medium  thick  r